===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|procrastinatio|prōcrāstinātiō|lang=la}}, from {{term|procrastino|prōcrāstinō|procrastinate|lang=la}}, from {{term|pro|prō|lang=la}} + {{term|crastinus|crāstinus|of tomorrow|lang=la}}, from {{term|cras|crās|tomorrow|lang=la}}.

